Word of caution: the above series of equations is not a logical series of steps, and is not part of any
proof, but is an informal technique used to help write the proof. We will select a value of δ so that
the last equation is true, and then use the last equation to prove the equations above it in turn (which
is what was meant earlier by working backwards).
